  "text": "Representatives from most of Latin America met in March 2019 and made an announcement, The Manaus Declaration on Histoplasmosis in the Americas and Caribbean, \"By 2025, every country should have access to rapid testing for histoplasmosis (antigen or PCR/ molecular)\". [CITATION_1] ",
